<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.8">
<l>nīyalaiyē ciṟupūvāy neṭumālārk keṉṟūtāy</l>
<l>nōyeṉatu nuvaleṉṉa nuvalātē yiruntoḻintāy</l>
<l>cāyaloṭu maṇimāmai taḷarntēṉā ṉiṉiyuṉatu</l>
<l>vāyalaki liṉṉaṭicil vaippārai nāṭāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[It’s] you, isn’t it, little mynah? When [I] said “as my messenger</l>
<l>to the great Māl talk of my pain”, without talking [of it] at all you stayed perched.</l>
<l>I dimmed in sapphire-darkness, along with [my] grace. Search now</l>
<l>for someone [else] to put sweet food in your beak.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
